<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no, viewport-fit=cover">
<title>Wizard — AgentulMeu</title>
<meta name="description" content="Generează 9 fișiere MD perfect configurate pentru agentul tău AI. Setup automat. Fără cod.">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --bg:#ffffff;--bg-2:#fafafa;--bg-3:#f5f5f5;
  --text:#0a0a0a;--text-2:#444;--text-3:#777;
  --gold:#C9A227;--gold-light:#E8C547;--gold-dark:#A68521;
  --gold-glow:rgba(201,162,39,0.12);
  --gold-gradient:linear-gradient(135deg,#C9A227,#E8C547,#C9A227);
  --gold-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(201,162,39,0.25);
  --gold-shadow-lg:0 16px 48px rgba(201,162,39,0.3);
  --green:#16a34a;--blue:#2563eb;--purple:#7c3aed;
  --border:rgba(0,0,0,0.06);--border-2:rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
  --shadow-sm:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  --shadow-md:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  --shadow-lg:0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  --shadow-xl:0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
  --radius:16px;--radius-lg:20px;--radius-xl:28px;
}
@keyframes fadeInUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
@keyframes float{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)}50%{transform:translateY(-6px)}}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.5}}
@keyframes shimmer{0%{background-position:-200% 0}100%{background-position:200% 0}}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;line-height:1.6}
.fade-in{animation:fadeInUp .6s ease-out both}
.float{animation:float 6s ease-in-out infinite}

/* ═══ NAV PREMIUM ═══ */
nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.88);backdrop-filter:blur(24px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.nav-inner{max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 32px;height:68px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.nav-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;text-decoration:none}
.nav-logo-icon{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:11px;background:var(--gold-gradient);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:800;font-size:1.05rem;color:#0a0a0a;box-shadow:var(--gold-shadow)}
.nav-logo-text{font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text)}
.nav-logo-text span{color:var(--gold)}
.nav-links{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:28px}
.nav-links a{color:var(--text-2);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:500;transition:color .2s}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--text)}
.btn-nav{padding:8px 18px;border-radius:10px;font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;transition:all .2s}
.btn-nav-ghost{color:var(--text);border:1px solid var(--border-2);background:transparent}
.btn-nav-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold-dark)}
.btn-nav-primary{background:var(--gold-gradient);color:#0a0a0a;box-shadow:var(--gold-shadow);border:none}
.btn-nav-primary:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:var(--gold-shadow-lg)}

/* ═══ HERO ═══ */
.hero{padding:120px 24px 60px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:-200px;right:-200px;width:500px;height:500px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(201,162,39,0.06) 0%,transparent 70%);border-radius:50%;pointer-events:none}
.hero-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:var(--gold-glow);border:1px solid rgba(201,162,39,0.2);border-radius:999px;padding:8px 18px 8px 12px;font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--gold-dark);margin-bottom:24px;animation:fadeInUp .6s ease-out both}
.hero-badge .dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);animation:pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite}
.hero h1{font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.2rem);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:16px;animation:fadeInUp .6s ease-out .1s both}
.hero h1 .gold{background:var(--gold-gradient);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text}
.hero p{color:var(--text-2);font-size:1.1rem;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 32px;line-height:1.7;animation:fadeInUp .6s ease-out .2s both}
.hero-cta{animation:fadeInUp .6s ease-out .3s both}

/* ═══ PREMIUM GOLD BUTTON ═══ */
.btn-gold{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
  padding:16px 36px;border-radius:14px;
  background:var(--gold-gradient);color:#0a0a0a;
  font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;
  box-shadow:var(--gold-shadow);border:none;cursor:pointer;
  transition:all .3s cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94);
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;
}
.btn-gold::before{
  content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:-100%;width:100%;height:100%;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(255,255,255,0.4),transparent);
  transition:left .6s ease;
}
.btn-gold:hover::before{left:100%}
.btn-gold:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:var(--gold-shadow-lg)}
.btn-gold:disabled{opacity:.5;cursor:not-allowed;transform:none!important}
.btn-gold:disabled::before{display:none}

.btn-outline{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
  padding:14px 28px;border-radius:14px;
  background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);
  font-size:0.92rem;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;
  border:1.5px solid var(--border-2);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);
  transition:all .3s ease;cursor:pointer;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;
}
.btn-outline:hover{border-color:var(--gold);box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(201,162,39,0.15);transform:translateY(-2px)}

/* ═══ FILES GRID PREMIUM ═══ */
.files-section{padding:0 24px 80px;max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;width:100%}
.files-section h2{font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.03em;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:center}
.files-section .subtitle{color:var(--text-2);font-size:0.95rem;text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px}

.files-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px}
.file-card{
  background:var(--bg);border:1.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:28px 24px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  transition:all .4s cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94);
}
.file-card::after{
  content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;
  background:var(--gold-gradient);opacity:0;transition:opacity .3s ease;
}
.file-card:hover{
  transform:translateY(-8px);box-shadow:var(--shadow-xl);
  border-color:rgba(201,162,39,0.2);
}
.file-card:hover::after{opacity:1}

.file-icon{
  width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;
  background:var(--gold-glow);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:16px;
}
.file-name{font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px}
.file-desc{font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-3);margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.5;min-height:36px}
.file-status{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;
  padding:5px 12px;border-radius:999px;
  font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:16px;
}
.file-status.pending{background:var(--bg-3);color:var(--text-3)}
.file-status.generating{background:var(--gold-glow);color:var(--gold-dark)}
.file-status.generating .dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);animation:pulse 1s ease-in-out infinite}
.file-status.done{background:rgba(22,163,74,0.08);color:var(--green);border:1px solid rgba(22,163,74,0.15)}

.file-actions{display:flex;gap:8px}
.file-actions .btn{flex:1;justify-content:center;padding:8px 12px;font-size:0.78rem;border-radius:10px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;border:none;font-family:Inter,sans-serif}
.file-actions .btn-generate{background:var(--gold-gradient);color:#0a0a0a;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(201,162,39,0.2);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.file-actions .btn-generate::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:-100%;width:100%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(255,255,255,0.3),transparent);transition:left .5s ease}
.file-actions .btn-generate:hover::before{left:100%}
.file-actions .btn-generate:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(201,162,39,0.3)}
.file-actions .btn-preview{background:var(--bg-3);color:var(--text)}
.file-actions .btn-preview:hover{background:var(--border)}
.file-actions .btn-download{background:var(--green);color:#fff}
.file-actions .btn-download:hover{opacity:.85}

/* ═══ FAQ ═══ */
.faq-section{padding:0 24px 80px;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;width:100%}
.faq-section h2{font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.03em;margin-bottom:32px;text-align:center}
.faq-item{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:20px 0}
.faq-question{font-weight:600;font-size:0.95rem;cursor:pointer;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;transition:color .2s}
.faq-question:hover{color:var(--gold-dark)}
.faq-answer{color:var(--text-2);font-size:0.88rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:12px;display:none}
.faq-item.open .faq-answer{display:block}
.faq-item.open .faq-toggle{transform:rotate(45deg)}
.faq-toggle{font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--text-3);transition:transform .3s ease}

/* ═══ FOOTER ═══ */
footer{text-align:center;padding:32px;color:var(--text-3);font-size:0.78rem;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}

/* ═══ RESPONSIVE ═══ */
@media(max-width:900px){
  .files-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
  .nav-links{display:none}
}
@media(max-width:600px){
  .files-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .hero{padding:100px 16px 40px}
  .files-section,.faq-section{padding:0 16px 60px}
}
</style>
  
  
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/assets/uploads/logoagentulmeu/favicon.png">
  <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/assets/uploads/logoagentulmeu/favicon.ico">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/mobile-app.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="main-content">


<nav class="nav-mobile">
  <a href="/" class="logo">Agentul<span style="color:var(--text)">Meu</span></a>
  <button class="hamburger" onclick="document.getElementById("mobile-menu").classList.toggle("open")">☰</button>
</nav>
<div id="mobile-menu" class="mobile-menu">
  <a href="/">Acasă</a>
  <a href="/wizard-form">Wizard</a>
  <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
  <a href="/install-page">Instalare</a>
  <a href="/docs">Docs</a>
  <a href="/login">Autentificare</a>
</div>
<div class="bottom-nav">
  <a href="/" class="active"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10 20v-6h4v6h5v-8h3L12 3 2 12h3v8z"/></svg>Acasă</a>
  <a href="/wizard-form"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 3H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-5 14H7v-2h7v2zm3-4H7v-2h10v2zm0-4H7V7h10v2z"/></svg>Wizard</a>
  <a href="/dashboard"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 13h8V3H3v10zm0 8h8v-6H3v6zm10 0h8V11h-8v10zm0-18v6h8V3h-8z"/></svg>Dashboard</a>
  <a href="/docs"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14 2H6c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L4 20c0 1.1.89 2 1.99 2H18c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V8l-6-6zm2 16H8v-2h8v2zm0-4H8v-2h8v2zm-3-5V3.5L18.5 9H13z"/></svg>Docs</a>
  <a href="/login"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/></svg>Cont</a>
</div>
<style>
.mobile-menu { position: fixed; top: 60px; right: -100%; width: 260px; height: calc(100vh - 60px); background: var(--dark-2); transition: 0.3s; z-index: 998; padding: 20px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; box-shadow: -4px 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
.mobile-menu.open { right: 0; }
.mobile-menu a { color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; padding: 14px; border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); font-weight: 500; }
.mobile-menu a:hover { background: rgba(212,175,55,0.15); color: var(--gold); }
</style>


<main style="flex:1">
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge"><span class="dot"></span> Wizard 8 Pași · AI Assist · Gratuit</div>
    <h1>Telefonul tău<br>devine cel mai <span class="gold">bun angajat</span></h1>
    <p>Generează 9 fișiere MD perfect configurate pentru agentul tău AI. Setup automat pe Android sau VPS. Fără cod. Fără complicații.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta" style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-gold">📁 Completează Cele 9 Fișiere Gratuit</a>
      <a href="/install-page" class="btn-outline">⚡ Instalare pe VPS</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FILES GRID -->
  <section class="files-section">
    <h2>📁 Cele 9 Fișiere MD — Structură Completă</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">Fiecare fișier este generat cu AI assist, validat pentru consistență și gata de import în OpenClaw sau Hermes.</p>
    
    <div class="files-grid">
      <div class="file-card fade-in">
        <div class="file-icon">🎯</div>
        <div class="file-name">SOUL.md</div>
        <div class="file-desc">Misiune, valori, reguli absolute, autonomie</div>
        <div class="file-status pending">Negenerat</div>
        <div class="file-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-generate" onclick="window.location.href='/dashboard'">⚡ Generează</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="file-card fade-in" style="animation-delay:.1s">
        <div class="file-icon">🪪</div>
        <div class="file-name">IDENTITY.md</div>
        <div class="file-desc">Profil agent, ton, limbă, program de lucru</div>
        <div class="file-status pending">Negenerat</div>
        <div class="file-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-generate" onclick="window.location.href='/dashboard'">⚡ Generează</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="file-card fade-in" style="animation-delay:.2s">
        <div class="file-icon">👤</div>
        <div class="file-name">USER.md</div>
        <div class="file-desc">Profilul tău, preferințe, priorități 90 zile</div>
        <div class="file-status pending">Negenerat</div>
        <div class="file-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-generate" onclick="window.location.href='/dashboard'">⚡ Generează</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="file-card fade-in" style="animation-delay:.3s">
        <div class="file-icon">🧠</div>
        <div class="file-name">MEMORY.md</div>
        <div class="file-desc">Context business, produse, prețuri, USP</div>
        <div class="file-status pending">Negenerat</div>
        <div class="file-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-generate" onclick="window.location.href='/dashboard'">⚡ Generează</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="file-card fade-in" style="animation-delay:.4s">
        <div class="file-icon">🛠️</div>
        <div class="file-name">TOOLS.md</div>
        <div class="file-desc">Canale, CRM, API-uri AI, buget, comenzi</div>
        <div class="file-status pending">Negenerat</div>
        <div class="file-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-generate" onclick="window.location.href='/dashboard'">⚡ Generează</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="file-card fade-in" style="animation-delay:.5s">
        <div class="file-icon">🤖</div>
        <div class="file-name">AGENTS.md</div>
        <div class="file-desc">Echipa de sub-agenți, workflow-uri, pipeline</div>
        <div class="file-status pending">Negenerat</div>
        <div class="file-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-generate" onclick="window.location.href='/dashboard'">⚡ Generează</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="file-card fade-in" style="animation-delay:.6s">
        <div class="file-icon">💓</div>
        <div class="file-name">HEARTBEAT.md</div>
        <div class="file-desc">Task-uri proactive, rutine, trigger-e, alerte</div>
        <div class="file-status pending">Negenerat</div>
        <div class="file-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-generate" onclick="window.location.href='/dashboard'">⚡ Generează</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="file-card fade-in" style="animation-delay:.7s">
        <div class="file-icon">🚀</div>
        <div class="file-name">BOOTSTRAP.md</div>
        <div class="file-desc">Checklist lansare, pași critici, fallback plan</div>
        <div class="file-status pending">Negenerat</div>
        <div class="file-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-generate" onclick="window.location.href='/dashboard'">⚡ Generează</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="file-card fade-in" style="animation-delay:.8s">
        <div class="file-icon">🔬</div>
        <div class="file-name">AGENT_RD.md</div>
        <div class="file-desc">Research framework, validare idei, surse</div>
        <div class="file-status pending">Negenerat</div>
        <div class="file-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-generate" onclick="window.location.href='/dashboard'">⚡ Generează</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <h2>❓ Întrebări Frecvente</h2>
    
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
        Am nevoie de cunoștințe tehnice?
        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">Nu. Wizard-ul este complet ghidat. Fiecare pas are explicații clare și sugestii AI. Instalarea se face cu o singură comandă.</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
        Ce se întâmplă cu datele mele?
        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">Totul rulează pe VPS-ul tău. Datele nu pleacă nicăieri — 100% self-hosted. Tu deții totul.</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
        Pot migra de la OpenClaw la Hermes?
        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">Da! Hermes are comanda <code style="background:var(--bg-2);padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--green)">hermes claw migrate</code> care importă automat configurația din OpenClaw.</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
        Cât durează generarea fișierelor?
        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">Aproximativ 15 minute pentru toate cele 9 fișiere. AI-ul generează fiecare modul individual, iar tu poți face preview și edita înainte de download.</div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer>© 2026 AgentulMeu.online · Made in România 🇷🇴</footer>

<script>
// Nav scroll effect
window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
  document.querySelector('nav').classList.toggle('scrolled', window.scrollY > 20);
});
</script>
</div>
</body>
</html>
